<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Voter Credentials</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <h1>{{title}}</h1>

    <p>Hi {{firstname}} {{lastname}}, heres your voter credentials</p>
    <p>Voter ID: <b>{{voterId}}</b></p>
    <p>Pin: <b>{{pin}}</b></p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p>The election will launch exactly
      {{election_date}}, proceed to this link to vote:
      <a href="{{election_link}}" target="_blank">Click here</a></p>
    <br />

    <small>Dont send this email to anyone, and dont reply in this email. Thank
      you.</small>
  </body>
</html>